OL,7,FKris Jepson speaks to Business
OL,8,FSecretary Kemi Badenoch on her visit
OL,9,Fto Teesside.
OL,11,FThe Business Secretary has told ITV
OL,12,FNews Tyne Tees that the government
OL,13,Fwants to build a new British Steel
OL,14,Felectric arc furnace "very quickly",
OL,15,Fbut said it "has to be right for the
OL,16,Ftaxpayer".
