OL,3,CBadenoch: Teesside electric arc
OL,4,Cfurnace has to be 'right for the
OL,5,Ctaxpayer'
OL,7,FKemi Badenoch visited the British
OL,8,FSteel site in Lackenby on Friday 10
OL,9,FMay and was joined by Tees Valley
OL,10,FMayor, Ben Houchen, and local Tory
OL,11,FMPs, Simon Clarke and Jacob Young.
OL,13,FNo announcement was made during the
OL,14,Fvisit, but when asked why there
OL,15,Fappears to be a delay in the new
OL,16,Felectric arc furnace being built, she
OL,17,Ftold ITV News the "discussions" are
OL,18,Fstill ongoing with British Steel.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
