OL,3,CBadenoch: Teesside electric arc
OL,4,Cfurnace has to be 'right for the
OL,5,Ctaxpayer'
OL,7,FShe said: "We need to make sure that
OL,8,Fthe deal we come to is one that is
OL,9,Fright for taxpayers, right for the
OL,10,Fpeople of Teesside, but also one that
OL,11,Fwe know is going to deliver
OL,12,Fcontinuously for the future.
OL,14,F"(The government support funding) is
OL,15,Fsomething we are acting on. We want do
OL,16,Fthis very quickly. This is a site that
OL,17,Fneeds that regeneration. We're really
OL,18,Fexcited about the plans to build the
OL,19,Felectric arc furnace, but we need to
OL,20,Fmake sure that we get it right."
