OL,3,CBadenoch: Teesside electric arc
OL,4,Cfurnace has to be 'right for the
OL,5,Ctaxpayer'
OL,7,FThe arc furnace was granted planning
OL,8,Fpermission in April, but detailed
OL,9,Fdesigns are yet to be finalised,
OL,10,Fraising the question of whether the
OL,11,F#300m government support package to
OL,12,Fmake it happen will be made available
OL,13,Fbefore the General Election.
OL,15,FWhen asked about that the Prime
OL,16,FMinister needed to control of the
OL,17,Fparty who were "fighting with each
OL,18,Fother like rats in a sack", she said
OL,19,Fthis was not the reason why the arc
OL,20,Ffurnace build has not started yet.
