OL,3,CBadenoch: Teesside electric arc
OL,4,Cfurnace has to be 'right for the
OL,5,Ctaxpayer'
OL,7,FShe said: "No, not at all. The party
OL,8,Fis definitely united. We are committed
OL,9,Fto steel in the UK. We want to make
OL,10,Fsure that we still have steel making
OL,11,Fcapability. It's part of our national
OL,12,Fresilience.
OL,14,F"I think the point Ben Houchen was
OL,15,Fmaking is correct, that parties need
OL,16,Fto be united. What we are seeing right
OL,17,Fnow is, after 14 years of government,
OL,18,Fpeople have different opinions, but
OL,19,Fthat doesn't mean that it's fighting."
